These variables hold info about the last chosen menu-entry (type is program) Info is written as is into memory during a user session. Info may be shown in debug-windows. The following Formats are used: Menupath is '>' separated A.>B.>C. Domain is ';'Separated: Code;Description Program is ';'Separated: PublicName; Id Project is ';' Separated: Code;Description
